{"tid":246900,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人屋企呀媽係淨係煮兩樣餸？","createTime":"2017-05-17T11:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T08:00:26.000Z","uid":6337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a9208bd00f3d0b17a9e925a5a17365596e6eac5","tid":246900,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:16:14.000Z","msg":"星期一  煎蛋角<br />\n星期二  絲瓜炒肉片<br />\n星期三  青瓜炒肉片<br />\n星期四  蝦醬蒸肉片<br />\n星期五  食前一晚食剩既肉片<br />\n星期六日唔煮食外賣<br />\n<br />\n平時我家姐做sales一個禮拜得一晚係屋企食<br />\n我見我媽每個禮拜有家姐食飯個晚就會煎多兩隻蛋<br />\n姐係家姐食親屋企飯都係食煎蛋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a23ca0c8c713de83f0c737c1f69af1bcab7150","tid":246900,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"長期肉片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4cbd16684ec7af46fbf4b85cf8425c462fa7495","tid":246900,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長期肉片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實都會蒸白切雞食<br />\n如果係蒸雞會食足3晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5852e8fb56a49a24271169347b07a3b548d961aa","tid":246900,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05